item.title: Creating a 317 safe training zone help plz
item.dc:creator: @SirPali SirPali
item.description:
@SirPali wrote:

public boolean nonWild() {
        if ((absX >= 3249 && absX <= 3258 && absY >= 3438 && absY <= 3431)
                || (absX >= 2816 && absX <= 2874 && absY >= 9822 && absY <= 9854)
                || (absX >= 3084 && absX <= 3088 && absY >= 3923 && absY <= 3940)
                || (absX >= 3092 && absX <= 3118 && absY >= 3914 && absY <= 3915)
                || (absX >= 3123 && absX <= 3126 && absY >= 3920 && absY <= 3944)
                || (absX >= 3774 && absX <= 7777 && absY >= 3950 && absY <= 3952)
                || (absX >= 2435 && absX <= 3156 && absY >= 2445 && absY <= 3166)
                || (absX >= 3249 && absX <= 3259 && absY >= 3471 && absY <= 3488)
                || (absX >= 2811 && absX <= 3293 && absY >= 3307 && absY <= 3823)

You switched the X-coordinates around. A coordinate can’t be bigger then 3293, but smaller then 2811… It’s just not possible.
